# =============================================================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# =============================================================================
# 
# IMPORTANT SECURITY CONSIDERATIONS:
# 
# 1. Never commit real API keys to version control
# 2. Use different keys for development, staging, and production
# 3. Regularly rotate API keys and secrets
# 4. Limit API key permissions to minimum required scope
# 5. Monitor API key usage for suspicious activity
# 6. Use environment variables in deployment platforms (Vercel, Netlify, etc.)
# 7. Enable CORS properly in your backend API
# 8. Use HTTPS in production for all API endpoints
# 9. Implement rate limiting on your API endpoints
# 10. Validate and sanitize all user inputs
# 
# =============================================================================